                            PASSING SHOT
                               
                              
                                DOCS
                                 BY
                          JOHN  OF S.H.A.G.
			*******************


Use joystick to control the players.the first joystick port controls the
female player, the second port controls the male.

To play doubles, both players should press fire and enter their initals.

The joystick directions control the players movement,when the fire button is pressed 
pressed the joystick directions control the shot.

With FIRE pressed:

FORWARD = FLAT

LEFT = SLICE

RIGHT = TOP SPIN

BACK = LOB

To serve, the joystick should be pushed in the appropriate direction for the
type of stroke when the ball flashes.

P = PAUSE
S = UNPAUSE
SHIFT + Q = QUIT GAME (once rally starts).



                     HOW TO PLAY PASSING SHOT

Press FIRE to start. If you wish to play doubles the FIRE must be pressed on
both sets of controls. Input your initials, then select the difficulty level
---higher levels start you futher into the world stages and put you up against
tougher opposition.

PASSING SHOT lets you play the deciding set in a three set match. If you play
doubles then the two players are on the same side, against the computer
computer conrtolled doubles pairs. The tramlines are in-bounds  when playing
doubles.


PASSING SHOT FOLLOWS THE NORMAL RULESS OF TENNIS. And incorporates all the
usual features.
You are required to reach six games to win the set, as per rules of tennis.
If you manage to win the match, the next round will take place at another 
location in the world.









